            <ul>
                <li>Navigate to the directory containing the Rest By Example file and use the <b>r2m</b> tool to generate Mobile APIs
                    into the <b>Mobile</b> directory.
                <pre>&gt; r2m gen -e example.txt</pre>
                </li>
                <li>The instructions to import the SDK and invoke the API for each platform are available on GitHub at <a href="https://github.com/magnetsystems/r2m-cli#invoking-the-mobile-api">Invoking the Mobile API</a>.</li>
            </ul>
